sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant Nyx as nyxclaw
    participant ZC as ZeroClaw
    participant LLM as OpenAI (gpt-4o)

    App->>Nyx: audio (PCM16 @ 24kHz)
    Nyx->>Nyx: VAD + STT → transcript
    Nyx->>ZC: {"type":"message","content":"What is the Wikipedia page for Rome?"}
    Note over Nyx,ZC: WebSocket /ws/avatar

    ZC->>LLM: chat completion (response_format: {speech, content})

    Note over ZC: Agent loop — LLM may call tools
    ZC-->>Nyx: {"type":"tool_call","name":"shell","args":{...}}
    ZC-->>Nyx: {"type":"tool_result","name":"shell","output":"..."}

    Note over ZC: LLM returns final JSON
    LLM->>ZC: {"speech":"Here's the page.","content":"**Rome**\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rome"}

    Note over ZC: Avatar channel parses JSON
    ZC->>Nyx: {"type":"speech_chunk","content":"Here's the page."}
    ZC->>Nyx: {"type":"rich_content","content":"**Rome**\nhttps://..."}
    ZC->>Nyx: {"type":"done","full_response":"Here's the page."}

    Note over Nyx: nyxclaw routes each event
    Nyx->>Nyx: speech_chunk → TTS → wav2arkit
    Nyx->>App: sync_frame (audio + blendshapes)
    Nyx->>App: transcript_delta (speech text only)
    Nyx->>App: rich_content (markdown content)
    Nyx->>App: transcript_done

    Note over App: App renders
    App->>App: sync_frame → avatar lip-syncs
    App->>App: transcript_delta → text bubble
    App->>App: rich_content → chat view + card
